{"tid":700641,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日拉麵『彩』","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T03:19:37.000Z","uid":138155,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e12775f0414d73b75c45c6fab86460de70b4b3aa","tid":700641,"uid":138155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:14:59.000Z","msg":"事源前日行咗十幾個鐘由油塘去屯門。除咗諗住當做運動之外，另一個目的就係諗住去食拉麵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/697248/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/697248/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n只係可惜行到去屯門附近已經冇哂力，邊度都唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。咁今日放工之後即刻搭車入去試個蝦味啉沾麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/210604_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F210604_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b50efb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗰湯同嗰麵底幾有驚喜，呢個價錢味道嚟講屌打一幻，雖然之後唔會好突登再入去元朗食，但係整體都算係中上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a46501222d050ca53820feac524ace1ab1a9ce","tid":700641,"uid":71505,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"右手個碟係茶記拎過來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e609b3a5be62bc9c6a3594015f2971d9c082f74","tid":700641,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"個麪係咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbde5bbb5a73c15856579e2977f66e5e5d4e753","tid":700641,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"呢間好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c2599d4c79a01e24c103ea5b945921369b78a0","tid":700641,"uid"